1
00:01:33,370 --> 00:01:34,780
[OVERDO]

2
00:01:35,420 --> 00:01:37,789
[Episode 4]

3
00:02:00,310 --> 00:02:04,500
[Spirit tablet of
the late respected father, Murong Feng]

4
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:10,139
Father's been gone for over a decade,

5
00:02:10,710 --> 00:02:13,470
yet you still carry his finger bone

6
00:02:13,630 --> 00:02:15,160
and pay respects every day.

7
00:02:15,470 --> 00:02:17,560
You're even more inseparable from him

8
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:19,030
than when he was alive.

9
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:22,780
They say burial brings peace,

10
00:02:24,310 --> 00:02:26,120
but I just can't bear the thought

11
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:28,290
of your father being all alone.

12
00:02:29,190 --> 00:02:30,590
With him by my side,

13
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,590
I can still talk to him.

14
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:34,520
But when Father was alive,

15
00:02:35,030 --> 00:02:36,910
he rarely talked to you.

16
00:02:39,630 --> 00:02:40,630
My stupid mouth.

17
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,120
Mother,

18
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,150
you and Father

19
00:02:44,870 --> 00:02:47,079
wished to be lovebirds in life

20
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:49,630
and conjoined twins in death.

21
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:52,030
-How touching!
-With your half-baked knowledge,

22
00:02:52,030 --> 00:02:53,560
don't embarrass yourself.

23
00:02:54,430 --> 00:02:55,030
I...

24
00:03:03,310 --> 00:03:04,560
Since you were little,

25
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:06,020
I didn't raise you myself,

26
00:03:06,710 --> 00:03:08,040
so you picked up this...

27
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,430
this rustic vulgarity.

28
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,080
I don't blame you.

29
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,460
But you're not young anymore.

30
00:03:15,870 --> 00:03:17,329
Your every word and action

31
00:03:17,430 --> 00:03:19,160
represents the Murong family.

32
00:03:19,910 --> 00:03:22,360
You must act like a proper lady.

33
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,090
Where's Fang Mulan?

34
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:50,240
This girl from Nanyang

35
00:03:50,590 --> 00:03:52,450
really doesn't know any manners.

36
00:03:52,710 --> 00:03:53,400
It's almost noon,

37
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,800
yet she's still not here.

38
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,500
From a merchant family

39
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,190
far away in Nanyang,

40
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:00,710
she indeed lacks manners.

41
00:04:01,630 --> 00:04:02,960
If Father were here,

42
00:04:03,630 --> 00:04:06,030
he'd never accept such a daughter-in-law.

43
00:04:08,470 --> 00:04:10,670
But for the future of our Murong family,

44
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,410
the Fang family's power

45
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,280
is too good to give up.

46
00:04:14,630 --> 00:04:15,800
We still must educate her

47
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:17,260
on the rules of our family.

48
00:04:18,070 --> 00:04:20,120
Teach that country bumpkin

49
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:23,090
how to respect her mother-in-law,

50
00:04:23,390 --> 00:04:24,560
serve her husband,

51
00:04:24,750 --> 00:04:26,430
and wait on her sister-in-law.

52
00:04:26,430 --> 00:04:28,070
As the old saying goes,

53
00:04:28,190 --> 00:04:30,390
"The character of a good wife and mother

54
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:32,680
is built on enduring grievances."

55
00:04:36,430 --> 00:04:37,159
Madam.

56
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:42,700
Madam, Young Miss Jinrui,

57
00:04:43,190 --> 00:04:44,450
Miss Fang has arrived.

58
00:04:46,630 --> 00:04:47,720
Miss, please.

59
00:04:56,750 --> 00:04:57,680
This way, Miss.

60
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:13,560
Who are you?

61
00:05:14,070 --> 00:05:16,230
[In German] Hello, I'm Anastasia.

62
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,040
Miss.

63
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:27,920
I'm Tasia, a close friend of Miss Fang's.

64
00:05:28,270 --> 00:05:30,730
Before she steps into
the Murong residence,

65
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,310
I'm here to confirm

66
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:34,750
if this new environment

67
00:05:34,750 --> 00:05:36,800
meets her daily living standards,

68
00:05:37,190 --> 00:05:39,650
[In German] according to German standards.

69
00:05:41,070 --> 00:05:41,920
Where is she?

70
00:05:42,070 --> 00:05:43,400
She'll be here shortly.

71
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:44,750
If possible,

72
00:05:44,830 --> 00:05:46,720
I'll put her luggage away first.

73
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,510
That's all?

74
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,250
All sizzle and no steak.

75
00:05:54,630 --> 00:05:56,600
And they call themselves
the shipping magnates of Nanyang?

76
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:58,310
It's as if some impoverished person

77
00:05:58,310 --> 00:06:00,430
came here to sponge off us.

78
00:06:13,870 --> 00:06:14,800
Oh my.

79
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:19,190
I wonder if the room
prepared for Miss Fang

80
00:06:19,190 --> 00:06:20,320
is spacious enough.

81
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,630
There's more?

82
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:22,600
So many.

83
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:33,920
We came in a hurry.

84
00:06:34,159 --> 00:06:35,890
Please excuse the meagerness.

85
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:38,310
What rich merchant?

86
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:40,680
Just an upstart.

87
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:45,450
Come and see, everyone.

88
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:47,560
This painting isn't even finished.

89
00:06:47,870 --> 00:06:49,000
Not even colored,

90
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,930
yet they're in a hurry to move it in.

91
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:54,560
This is a work
by a famous European painter,

92
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:57,000
a great masterpiece.

93
00:06:58,430 --> 00:07:00,040
When this painting was acquired,

94
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:02,190
Miss Fang was only 10 years old.

95
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:07,290
Take it away.

96
00:07:13,070 --> 00:07:13,870
Young Master.

97
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,190
The investigator just replied.

98
00:07:16,190 --> 00:07:18,310
The Fang family in Nanyang
started in the sugar industry,

99
00:07:18,310 --> 00:07:20,160
and then got involved in
coffee, shipping, mining,

100
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:20,920
and so on.

101
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,000
Fang Mulan is

102
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:24,560
indeed the only daughter
of the Fang family.

103
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:26,240
Miss Fang grew up in Nanyang.

104
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:28,130
She came to China this time,

105
00:07:28,190 --> 00:07:30,310
first, for her marriage
with Young Master Qingyu,

106
00:07:30,310 --> 00:07:31,680
and, second, to pave the way

107
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:33,830
for expanding their business in Nancheng.

108
00:07:33,830 --> 00:07:35,890
We've yet to find any issues with her.

109
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,120
Young Master Qingyi.

110
00:07:37,390 --> 00:07:38,920
Is she really that Ren Susu?

111
00:07:43,750 --> 00:07:45,950
It's a pity that in the Beicheng clinic,

112
00:07:46,430 --> 00:07:48,360
I didn't get the chance to meet her.

113
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:50,240
Don't worry.

114
00:07:51,510 --> 00:07:54,040
There will be plenty of chances
to see her now.

115
00:07:56,310 --> 00:07:58,070
Moving into her husband's home
is a big day.

116
00:07:58,070 --> 00:08:00,310
Instead of coming to
pay respects to the elders,

117
00:08:00,310 --> 00:08:01,240
where did she go?

118
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:04,120
She naturally has
more important things to do

119
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:06,120
than paying respects to the elders.

120
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:10,950
Principal.

121
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:15,000
This is the invitation list
for the aviation school's opening.

122
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:16,600
We've sent invitations
to all major families

123
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,480
in Nancheng.

124
00:08:17,870 --> 00:08:19,570
But the Li family's patriarch
claims to be ill.

125
00:08:19,570 --> 00:08:21,960
[Zhenhua No. 1 Aviation School]

126
00:08:19,950 --> 00:08:21,390
The Zhang and Huo families say

127
00:08:21,390 --> 00:08:23,120
they're swamped with business.

128
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:24,390
If these 3 families don't attend,

129
00:08:24,390 --> 00:08:26,160
those fence-sitters will

130
00:08:26,510 --> 00:08:28,170
also find excuses not to come.

131
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:31,120
The aviation school was established

132
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:32,840
with patriotic aspiration.

133
00:08:33,789 --> 00:08:34,390
It was only

134
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:37,049
out of respect for the Murongs that

135
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:38,669
they showed up automatically

136
00:08:38,669 --> 00:08:40,070
to express their stance.

137
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:41,630
But now,

138
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:43,960
in the vast Nancheng,

139
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:46,440
how many families have business dealings

140
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,510
with foreigners?

141
00:08:48,550 --> 00:08:50,870
The aviation school is
a national salvation organization.

142
00:08:50,870 --> 00:08:53,130
They naturally want to avoid suspicion.

143
00:08:53,390 --> 00:08:56,150
But this aviation school's been
abandoned for so many years.

144
00:08:56,150 --> 00:08:57,600
It's only after you took over

145
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:59,260
that it got on the right track,

146
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:01,890
training the first batch
of decent students.

147
00:09:01,910 --> 00:09:03,960
Now's the time
to leverage this opening ceremony

148
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:06,000
to attract financial support
and networking help

149
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,240
from all sectors.

150
00:09:07,390 --> 00:09:07,870
They...

151
00:09:08,270 --> 00:09:09,080
Don't worry.

152
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,670
I will resolve this.

153
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:17,790
Qingyu.

154
00:09:20,150 --> 00:09:21,080
Miss Fang.

155
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:23,080
Mulan,

156
00:09:23,630 --> 00:09:24,560
why are you here?

157
00:09:27,030 --> 00:09:28,030
You can leave now.

158
00:09:28,510 --> 00:09:29,200
Yes.

159
00:09:34,750 --> 00:09:35,910
You've been too busy lately

160
00:09:35,910 --> 00:09:37,040
and skipping meals.

161
00:09:37,630 --> 00:09:39,240
I bought your favorite
dried bamboo shoot buns.

162
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:39,970
Have a taste.

163
00:09:41,390 --> 00:09:42,520
You've worked hard.

164
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,360
Not at all.

165
00:09:44,630 --> 00:09:45,480
You're the one

166
00:09:45,790 --> 00:09:48,190
working hard running the aviation school.

167
00:09:49,630 --> 00:09:50,890
You heard everything?

168
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:51,920
It's fine.

169
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,970
There's always a solution.

170
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,970
The Huo, Zhang, and Li families

171
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:04,360
have all been invited,

172
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:07,550
but it's unsure that

173
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:09,100
everyone will show up.

174
00:10:09,670 --> 00:10:10,550
I will host

175
00:10:10,790 --> 00:10:11,910
an engagement party

176
00:10:11,910 --> 00:10:12,960
at home.

177
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,000
When the time comes,

178
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,360
I'll personally invite them to

179
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:17,560
attend the aviation school's opening.

180
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:20,670
Eat up

181
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:21,960
before it gets cold.

182
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:22,510
Okay.

183
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:34,510
All that fuss at home,

184
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:36,030
and the star of the show is here.

185
00:10:36,030 --> 00:10:37,230
What brings you here?

186
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:43,000
It's nothing.

187
00:10:44,150 --> 00:10:46,240
Just that the immense wealth
of my sister-in-law's family

188
00:10:46,240 --> 00:10:48,500
has made my older sister green with envy.

189
00:10:50,870 --> 00:10:51,840
You know what,

190
00:10:52,510 --> 00:10:54,600
when it comes to
agitating my older sister,

191
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:56,200
you and I are on the same page.

192
00:10:58,670 --> 00:10:59,360
Yeah.

193
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:02,150
If people weren't making trouble
for your older brother,

194
00:11:02,150 --> 00:11:02,910
why'd he be so busy

195
00:11:02,910 --> 00:11:04,970
that he doesn't even have time to eat?

196
00:11:06,480 --> 00:11:08,360
You really care about my brother.

197
00:11:09,030 --> 00:11:11,030
How did my family get so lucky

198
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:13,540
to have such a good daughter-in-law?

199
00:11:14,870 --> 00:11:16,480
I'm your brother's fiancée.

200
00:11:16,630 --> 00:11:18,090
Of course I care about him.

201
00:11:24,150 --> 00:11:25,000
All right.

202
00:11:25,550 --> 00:11:27,010
Are you going to let me eat?

203
00:11:27,870 --> 00:11:28,440
Wait.

204
00:11:30,030 --> 00:11:30,670
Qingyu.

205
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:33,700
So many people want to
trip up our family.

206
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:35,360
You can't just eat food

207
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:36,690
brought by an outsider.

208
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:40,240
How is Mulan an outsider?

209
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:42,080
In these troubled times,

210
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:43,680
you can never be too careful.

211
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:45,850
Let me test it for poison first.

212
00:11:55,270 --> 00:11:56,720
Buns from Rongxinji.

213
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,320
You're amazing.

214
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:00,750
It's your first time in Nancheng,

215
00:12:00,750 --> 00:12:04,280
and you already found such an authentic
and hidden gem of a shop.

216
00:12:07,390 --> 00:12:08,840
It's not hard to find out

217
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:10,240
what Qingyu likes to eat.

218
00:12:11,390 --> 00:12:12,590
I love their food too.

219
00:12:12,790 --> 00:12:14,360
Please remember that as well.

220
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:15,820
You can go buy it yourself.

221
00:12:17,390 --> 00:12:18,630
Since you say so,

222
00:12:19,030 --> 00:12:21,720
I can only come here
to steal my brother's food.

223
00:12:24,790 --> 00:12:26,120
You won't be mad, right?

224
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:30,160
You're getting more and more childish.

225
00:12:33,030 --> 00:12:34,200
I have other things to do.

226
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:34,960
I have to go.

227
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:37,390
I'll send you back.

228
00:12:37,390 --> 00:12:38,150
It's fine.

229
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:39,030
What,

230
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:41,010
do you dislike me that much?

231
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:42,510
What do you mean?

232
00:12:42,510 --> 00:12:43,440
Since you don't,

233
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:44,390
do me the honor

234
00:12:44,750 --> 00:12:45,810
of riding in my car.

235
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:48,180
We'll be a family soon, after all.

236
00:12:48,550 --> 00:12:50,360
We should bond, don't you think?

237
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:04,750
Miss Fang.

238
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:06,750
There's more rain

239
00:13:07,270 --> 00:13:09,270
in Nanyang than in Nancheng, right?

240
00:13:14,240 --> 00:13:16,360
If you like dry and sunny weather,

241
00:13:17,150 --> 00:13:18,670
you should head north.

242
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:21,080
At least

243
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:23,000
to places like Beicheng,

244
00:13:23,630 --> 00:13:25,030
where there's less rain.

245
00:13:28,510 --> 00:13:29,320
Miss Fang,

246
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:31,420
have you been to Beicheng?

247
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:33,910
Never been.

248
00:13:36,150 --> 00:13:38,440
I actually miss the weather in Beicheng.

249
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:40,130
I have an old friend,

250
00:13:40,960 --> 00:13:42,510
whom I met in Beicheng.

251
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:46,360
We were pretty close then.

252
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:47,670
Unfortunately,

253
00:13:48,720 --> 00:13:50,030
she died later.

254
00:13:52,030 --> 00:13:52,750
Is that so?

255
00:13:53,480 --> 00:13:54,240
Yes,

256
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:56,330
but she really deserved to die.

257
00:13:57,360 --> 00:13:58,790
If it weren't for her,

258
00:14:00,120 --> 00:14:02,520
I wouldn't have suffered
3 years in prison.

259
00:14:12,750 --> 00:14:14,880
Didn't know you have such a rough past.

260
00:14:16,390 --> 00:14:17,720
But the past is the past.

261
00:14:19,120 --> 00:14:20,180
Better to let it go.

262
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:21,550
Let it go?

263
00:14:22,750 --> 00:14:24,280
You're quite open-minded.

264
00:14:26,670 --> 00:14:27,870
By the way, Miss Fang,

265
00:14:28,910 --> 00:14:29,870
do you think

266
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:32,110
the dead can come back to life?

267
00:14:33,390 --> 00:14:34,960
Of course not.

268
00:14:36,720 --> 00:14:37,510
I also think

269
00:14:38,270 --> 00:14:40,130
the dead cannot come back to life.

270
00:14:40,840 --> 00:14:42,910
If that woman really came back to life,

271
00:14:42,910 --> 00:14:45,120
I'd make sure I send her to hell.

272
00:14:45,910 --> 00:14:46,790
Am I right?

273
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:58,000
But if that woman

274
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:01,080
can come back from the dead,

275
00:15:02,080 --> 00:15:03,720
how can you take her down?

276
00:15:08,390 --> 00:15:10,050
You must be joking, Miss Fang.

277
00:15:11,270 --> 00:15:13,000
If she really came back to life,

278
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:15,660
I wouldn't need to do anything at all.

279
00:15:16,600 --> 00:15:18,510
As long as I let others
see her true colors,

280
00:15:18,510 --> 00:15:21,110
someone will naturally
take care of her for me.

281
00:15:21,960 --> 00:15:22,910
Am I right,

282
00:15:24,080 --> 00:15:24,960
Ren Susu?

283
00:15:27,200 --> 00:15:28,360
Who is Ren Susu?

284
00:15:29,390 --> 00:15:31,650
No wonder you've been so weird around me.

285
00:15:31,720 --> 00:15:32,470
You're mistaken...

286
00:15:32,470 --> 00:15:34,000
Stop pretending.

287
00:15:36,630 --> 00:15:38,510
You stole the film negatives
of Huo Minxian

288
00:15:38,510 --> 00:15:40,170
and her paramour, didn't you?

289
00:15:40,600 --> 00:15:42,750
So you can win the Murong family's
trust and gratitude,

290
00:15:42,750 --> 00:15:44,350
stomping on me along the way.

291
00:15:44,630 --> 00:15:46,690
Even if I expose your true colors now,

292
00:15:46,750 --> 00:15:48,010
no one will believe me.

293
00:15:48,840 --> 00:15:49,670
Is that it?

294
00:15:51,510 --> 00:15:54,110
I really don't know
what you're talking about.

295
00:15:54,510 --> 00:15:55,960
Sure, deny it.

296
00:15:56,960 --> 00:15:59,670
You're an expert
at playing with people's hearts

297
00:15:59,670 --> 00:16:01,320
and sowing discord after all.

298
00:16:01,320 --> 00:16:02,840
But listen up, Ren Susu.

299
00:16:03,360 --> 00:16:04,480
No matter what your motive is

300
00:16:04,480 --> 00:16:06,200
in entering the Murong family,

301
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:06,910
the same thing

302
00:16:06,910 --> 00:16:08,710
will never happen a second time.

303
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:10,500
Before you make a move,

304
00:16:11,390 --> 00:16:12,790
I'll make sure everyone

305
00:16:13,670 --> 00:16:15,080
sees your true colors.

306
00:16:51,080 --> 00:16:52,280
Young Master Qingyi,

307
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:53,520
you guessed it right.

308
00:16:53,840 --> 00:16:55,670
Over the years,
Huo Mingxi's branch in Beicheng

309
00:16:55,670 --> 00:16:56,480
has scattered

310
00:16:56,630 --> 00:16:58,490
like monkeys when the tree falls.

311
00:16:58,600 --> 00:17:00,600
Not a single person who experienced

312
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:02,900
what happened back then
can be found.

313
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:08,960
She chose to come back,

314
00:17:10,160 --> 00:17:11,920
so she must be prepared.

315
00:17:13,270 --> 00:17:15,069
What happened to Huo Mingxi then

316
00:17:15,510 --> 00:17:17,240
caused you to suffer in prison,

317
00:17:17,880 --> 00:17:20,140
and even the tendons in your hand were...

318
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:24,480
If the Huos identify Miss Ren,

319
00:17:25,750 --> 00:17:27,410
with their ruthless methods,

320
00:17:29,110 --> 00:17:31,110
you'll certainly be avenged.

321
00:17:37,030 --> 00:17:38,090
Don't ever mention

322
00:17:38,790 --> 00:17:40,400
my injury to Qingyu.

323
00:17:42,240 --> 00:17:42,830
Noted.

324
00:17:44,960 --> 00:17:47,090
Even the best-laid plans can go wrong.

325
00:17:47,790 --> 00:17:49,120
Back when the Huo family

326
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:51,440
was hunting down Huo Mingxi's killer,

327
00:17:52,880 --> 00:17:54,440
a butler surnamed Li

328
00:17:54,680 --> 00:17:55,880
saw Ren Susu.

329
00:17:56,680 --> 00:17:58,000
He made a mistake later

330
00:17:58,830 --> 00:18:00,890
and was exiled to Feng'an by the Huos.

331
00:18:02,920 --> 00:18:04,580
Contact our people in Feng'an

332
00:18:05,160 --> 00:18:06,090
to find this man.

333
00:18:06,510 --> 00:18:07,440
And then?

334
00:18:09,790 --> 00:18:11,050
Bring him to Nancheng.

335
00:18:11,590 --> 00:18:12,830
It's time for him to

336
00:18:13,480 --> 00:18:15,110
meet his old masters.

337
00:18:20,270 --> 00:18:21,350
Ren Susu.

338
00:18:22,830 --> 00:18:24,200
I don't know why
you returned from the dead

339
00:18:24,200 --> 00:18:26,260
and are impersonating someone else,

340
00:18:26,680 --> 00:18:28,480
but I can use the Huos

341
00:18:29,030 --> 00:18:31,590
to bring the past to light again.

342
00:18:33,110 --> 00:18:34,170
When that happens,

343
00:18:34,400 --> 00:18:36,000
how will you deal with it?

344
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:40,200
Just exposing your facade

345
00:18:40,440 --> 00:18:41,680
is too boring.

346
00:18:42,640 --> 00:18:44,720
I want you to be encircled by enemies,

347
00:18:44,830 --> 00:18:46,160
isolated and helpless,

348
00:18:46,790 --> 00:18:48,590
begging me for mercy.

349
00:18:49,920 --> 00:18:51,000
In this round,

350
00:18:52,070 --> 00:18:54,880
I will make sure you admit defeat.

351
00:19:00,050 --> 00:19:02,550
[Nancheng Train Station]

352
00:19:06,370 --> 00:19:10,370
[Nancheng Station]

353
00:19:10,470 --> 00:19:14,680
[Nancheng Station]

354
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:27,550
Butler Li.

355
00:19:27,830 --> 00:19:28,400
Here.

356
00:19:28,790 --> 00:19:29,680
This family that's hiring,

357
00:19:29,680 --> 00:19:30,920
what business do they do?

358
00:19:30,920 --> 00:19:32,580
Follow me and you'll find out.

359
00:19:37,550 --> 00:19:38,200
Boss Hai?

360
00:19:38,310 --> 00:19:39,550
Boss Hai! Boss Hai!

361
00:19:39,260 --> 00:19:42,500
[Renowned opera star: Hai Tangqing]

362
00:19:39,550 --> 00:19:40,480
Boss Hai is here.

363
00:19:42,550 --> 00:19:43,950
A true Peking Opera star.

364
00:19:48,070 --> 00:19:49,640
Boss Hai!

365
00:19:54,680 --> 00:19:55,680
Please don't push!

366
00:19:55,680 --> 00:19:56,440
One by one!

367
00:19:56,590 --> 00:19:57,400
One by one!

368
00:19:57,960 --> 00:19:58,720
One by one!

369
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:00,960
What's going on?

370
00:20:01,160 --> 00:20:02,400
What is this about?

371
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:04,860
Where's yours?

372
00:20:05,480 --> 00:20:06,440
Didn't bring a notebook?

373
00:20:06,440 --> 00:20:07,100
No worries.

374
00:20:08,350 --> 00:20:09,010
No worries.

375
00:20:09,920 --> 00:20:10,960
Here, take it.

376
00:20:11,790 --> 00:20:12,650
Where's yours?

377
00:20:15,200 --> 00:20:15,730
Let's go.

378
00:20:15,750 --> 00:20:16,200
Let's get out.

379
00:20:16,200 --> 00:20:16,730
Boss Hai!

380
00:20:16,790 --> 00:20:17,400
Boss Hai!

381
00:20:18,480 --> 00:20:19,720
You're a shy one, huh?

382
00:20:20,310 --> 00:20:21,070
Boss Hai!

383
00:20:21,160 --> 00:20:22,200
Can I get your autograph too?

384
00:20:22,200 --> 00:20:22,720
Here.

385
00:20:25,790 --> 00:20:27,030
Nancheng and Feng'an are

386
00:20:27,030 --> 00:20:28,230
really worlds apart.

387
00:20:30,640 --> 00:20:31,720
My wallet's gone!

388
00:20:32,030 --> 00:20:32,510
Laiyi.

389
00:20:33,200 --> 00:20:34,000
Inspector Li.

390
00:20:34,720 --> 00:20:35,650
Why are you here?

391
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:37,720
Boss Hai came to Nancheng today.

392
00:20:37,720 --> 00:20:39,070
Our commissioner's wife

393
00:20:39,070 --> 00:20:40,310
is a big fan of hers,

394
00:20:40,590 --> 00:20:42,720
so she asked me to come maintain order.

395
00:20:44,240 --> 00:20:44,900
Who is this?

396
00:20:45,270 --> 00:20:46,070
Just in time.

397
00:20:46,510 --> 00:20:47,880
I lost my wallet.

398
00:20:48,640 --> 00:20:49,830
Please help me find it.

399
00:20:49,830 --> 00:20:50,750
Try to recall

400
00:20:51,240 --> 00:20:51,720
if anyone

401
00:20:51,720 --> 00:20:53,110
came into close contact with you.

402
00:20:53,110 --> 00:20:54,030
Did anyone touch you

403
00:20:54,030 --> 00:20:55,030
or bump into you?

404
00:20:55,350 --> 00:20:55,920
Yes.

405
00:20:56,240 --> 00:20:57,000
A woman

406
00:20:57,270 --> 00:20:58,350
surrounded by a crowd.

407
00:20:58,350 --> 00:21:00,010
I think she's an opera singer.

408
00:21:01,790 --> 00:21:02,310
Okay.

409
00:21:02,640 --> 00:21:03,590
I'll go find out.

410
00:21:05,400 --> 00:21:06,400
Losing a wallet is no big deal.

411
00:21:06,400 --> 00:21:08,110
Get in the car with me right now.

412
00:21:08,110 --> 00:21:09,400
Where are we going?

413
00:21:09,880 --> 00:21:10,440
Tonight, the Huos

414
00:21:10,440 --> 00:21:12,070
are attending a banquet
at my master's home.

415
00:21:12,070 --> 00:21:14,730
We're inviting you
to meet your former masters.

416
00:21:16,510 --> 00:21:18,880
My master belongs to
a collateral branch of the Huos.

417
00:21:18,880 --> 00:21:20,350
I have zero contact with the main branch

418
00:21:20,350 --> 00:21:21,640
of the Huos in Nancheng.

419
00:21:21,640 --> 00:21:23,370
They're not my former masters.

420
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:25,200
You've got the wrong person.

421
00:21:26,680 --> 00:21:28,610
You just need to identify someone.

422
00:21:28,920 --> 00:21:29,880
When the time comes,

423
00:21:29,880 --> 00:21:32,010
my master will reward you handsomely.

424
00:21:32,200 --> 00:21:33,160
Identify who?

425
00:21:33,350 --> 00:21:34,280
The real culprit

426
00:21:35,030 --> 00:21:36,890
who killed Huo Mingxi 3 years ago.

427
00:21:46,030 --> 00:21:47,760
Don't gather in public places!

428
00:21:48,070 --> 00:21:48,790
Disperse!

429
00:21:50,070 --> 00:21:51,750
Inspector Li said to disperse!

430
00:21:51,750 --> 00:21:52,480
Disperse!

431
00:21:56,880 --> 00:21:57,960
Boss Hai, don't go.

432
00:21:57,960 --> 00:21:59,290
It was finally our turn.

433
00:22:02,790 --> 00:22:04,590
Boss Hai!

434
00:22:05,720 --> 00:22:06,590
Boss Hai!

435
00:22:06,830 --> 00:22:07,720
Boss Hai!

436
00:22:08,640 --> 00:22:09,510
Boss Hai!

437
00:22:10,510 --> 00:22:11,400
Boss Hai!

438
00:22:13,030 --> 00:22:13,920
Boss Hai!

439
00:22:16,750 --> 00:22:18,590
Boss Hai!

440
00:22:18,790 --> 00:22:20,110
Don't go, Boss Hai!

441
00:22:20,350 --> 00:22:21,440
Wait for me!

442
00:22:22,030 --> 00:22:22,750
Boss Hai!

443
00:22:22,750 --> 00:22:23,880
Don't go, Boss Hai!

444
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:26,440
Boss Hai, we love you!

445
00:22:27,400 --> 00:22:27,830
Hey...

446
00:22:28,270 --> 00:22:28,750
You...

447
00:22:31,480 --> 00:22:32,410
Hide me for a bit.

448
00:23:10,750 --> 00:23:12,210
Thank you, Mr. Inspector.

449
00:23:13,070 --> 00:23:13,920
You're welcome.

450
00:23:13,920 --> 00:23:14,450
No, wait.

451
00:23:15,640 --> 00:23:16,970
Why did you run just now?

452
00:23:17,590 --> 00:23:18,750
Why did I run?

453
00:23:19,160 --> 00:23:19,960
If I didn't run,

454
00:23:19,960 --> 00:23:21,640
those fans would eat me alive.

455
00:23:23,160 --> 00:23:24,690
And why were you chasing me?

456
00:23:26,790 --> 00:23:28,270
Are you also my fan?

457
00:23:29,200 --> 00:23:29,790
No.

458
00:23:30,110 --> 00:23:30,590
I...

459
00:23:30,960 --> 00:23:33,090
If you are, just admit it.
Don't be shy.

460
00:23:35,830 --> 00:23:37,400
My pen was knocked away in the crowd,

461
00:23:37,400 --> 00:23:39,200
so I can't give you an autograph.

462
00:23:41,110 --> 00:23:41,680
I know!

463
00:23:55,030 --> 00:23:56,440
Take this as my autograph.

464
00:23:56,440 --> 00:23:57,070
Thank you.

465
00:24:00,270 --> 00:24:01,070
Wait a minute!

466
00:24:04,510 --> 00:24:05,110
What is it?

467
00:24:06,160 --> 00:24:07,420
Someone just reported

468
00:24:07,590 --> 00:24:09,680
that they suspect you stole their wallet.

469
00:24:09,680 --> 00:24:10,810
Please come with me.

470
00:24:11,240 --> 00:24:12,700
I'm a famous opera singer.

471
00:24:12,720 --> 00:24:14,440
Why'd I steal a passerby's wallet?

472
00:24:14,440 --> 00:24:16,900
I've seen plenty of wealthy kleptomaniacs.

473
00:24:18,960 --> 00:24:19,760
I'm not saying

474
00:24:19,830 --> 00:24:20,550
you took it.

475
00:24:20,550 --> 00:24:21,410
I'm just saying

476
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:23,790
you're not exempt from suspicion.

477
00:24:23,790 --> 00:24:25,390
Please cooperate with this.

478
00:24:26,880 --> 00:24:27,680
I knew it.

479
00:24:29,480 --> 00:24:31,200
My singing master was right.

480
00:24:32,030 --> 00:24:33,440
We opera singers...

481
00:24:35,160 --> 00:24:37,000
are always looked down upon.

482
00:24:37,640 --> 00:24:38,830
That's not what I meant.

483
00:24:38,830 --> 00:24:39,790
Mr. Inspector,

484
00:24:40,160 --> 00:24:41,490
if you don't believe me,

485
00:24:41,830 --> 00:24:43,360
you can search me right now!

486
00:24:44,110 --> 00:24:46,000
I may just be a lowly actor,

487
00:24:46,200 --> 00:24:47,400
but I'd never stoop so low

488
00:24:47,400 --> 00:24:49,330
as to do something shady like that.

489
00:24:49,350 --> 00:24:50,110
Search me!

490
00:24:50,480 --> 00:24:52,080
I'll strip for you to search.

491
00:24:52,270 --> 00:24:53,400
If you find nothing,

492
00:24:53,510 --> 00:24:54,550
just consider it

493
00:24:55,030 --> 00:24:56,880
a free performance
of "The Injustice to Dou E" for you.

494
00:24:56,880 --> 00:24:57,960
N-No, no.

495
00:24:58,200 --> 00:24:59,600
That won't be necessary.

496
00:25:01,000 --> 00:25:01,680
Boss Hai.

497
00:25:02,920 --> 00:25:04,000
I was wrong.

498
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:05,600
I'm sorry.

499
00:25:32,010 --> 00:25:33,010
Hello?

500
00:25:33,510 --> 00:25:35,240
Are the ordered flowers ready?

501
00:25:35,510 --> 00:25:36,920
Murong Qingyi's subordinate

502
00:25:36,920 --> 00:25:38,520
picked up a man from Feng'an.

503
00:25:40,400 --> 00:25:41,800
He has a Beicheng accent,

504
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:43,000
is around 50 years old,

505
00:25:42,040 --> 00:25:44,550
[Name: Li Cai]

506
00:25:43,310 --> 00:25:44,000
and his name

507
00:25:44,160 --> 00:25:44,750
is Li Cai.

508
00:25:44,920 --> 00:25:45,780
Do you know him?

509
00:25:48,750 --> 00:25:49,350
I do.

510
00:25:50,070 --> 00:25:50,830
Sure enough.

511
00:25:51,440 --> 00:25:53,030
I knew that Murong Qingyi

512
00:25:53,030 --> 00:25:54,750
wouldn't let you off so easily.

513
00:25:54,750 --> 00:25:55,680
What do we do now?

514
00:26:05,160 --> 00:26:06,160
I need the flowers

515
00:26:06,310 --> 00:26:07,720
for a family banquet.

516
00:26:08,440 --> 00:26:10,770
If there are any dead branches and leaves,

517
00:26:10,790 --> 00:26:12,520
wouldn't it bother the guests?

518
00:26:13,240 --> 00:26:14,200
Help me

519
00:26:14,750 --> 00:26:16,880
trim away everything inappropriate.

520
00:26:16,920 --> 00:26:17,590
Otherwise,

521
00:26:18,440 --> 00:26:19,680
I won't pay for them.

522
00:26:21,070 --> 00:26:22,590
I'm so sorry, Miss Fang.

523
00:26:22,830 --> 00:26:24,200
I'll have my people

524
00:26:24,200 --> 00:26:26,130
trim them clean for you right away.

525
00:26:34,350 --> 00:26:35,440
I heard you

526
00:26:35,550 --> 00:26:36,550
ordered flowers.

527
00:26:36,880 --> 00:26:37,350
Yes.

528
00:26:37,880 --> 00:26:39,010
Where are you going?

529
00:26:39,590 --> 00:26:40,520
Didn't you hear?

530
00:26:40,640 --> 00:26:41,310
I ordered flowers.

531
00:26:41,310 --> 00:26:42,910
The guests will arrive soon.

532
00:26:42,920 --> 00:26:43,920
Who will entertain the guests

533
00:26:43,920 --> 00:26:44,750
with you gone?

534
00:26:45,640 --> 00:26:46,310
What,

535
00:26:46,830 --> 00:26:49,890
is the Murong residence
short of people to take charge?

536
00:26:52,070 --> 00:26:54,000
No, it is not.

537
00:26:54,920 --> 00:26:56,980
It's short of an opera singer though.

538
00:26:58,440 --> 00:26:59,160
Miss Fang,

539
00:26:59,160 --> 00:27:01,820
I went to a lot of trouble
to set up a stage for you.

540
00:27:01,830 --> 00:27:02,880
It'd be a pity

541
00:27:03,400 --> 00:27:04,480
if you left.

542
00:27:20,070 --> 00:27:21,550
Today's meal at the Murongs'

543
00:27:21,550 --> 00:27:23,080
will surely be very boring.

544
00:27:25,510 --> 00:27:27,030
How about we leave early tonight,

545
00:27:27,030 --> 00:27:29,030
and I take you to Xanadu for some fun?

546
00:27:30,900 --> 00:27:35,310
[Zhang Mingshu,
Eldest Young Master of the Zhang family]

547
00:27:32,000 --> 00:27:32,680
No thanks.

548
00:27:33,400 --> 00:27:35,730
I have to go back
and take care of my father.

549
00:27:37,110 --> 00:27:38,030
Fine.

550
00:27:38,830 --> 00:27:40,440
I get it. You're a filial son,

551
00:27:40,960 --> 00:27:43,290
who has to take care
of your paralyzed dad.

552
00:27:43,790 --> 00:27:44,830
Suit yourself.

553
00:27:45,440 --> 00:27:46,770
I'll have fun by myself.

554
00:27:47,720 --> 00:27:49,750
I suggest
you keep a low profile tonight too.

555
00:27:49,750 --> 00:27:51,440
He's your future brother-in-law after all,

556
00:27:51,440 --> 00:27:52,900
but you show no care at all.

557
00:27:53,750 --> 00:27:55,070
His aviation school is opening,

558
00:27:55,070 --> 00:27:56,590
but you keep dragging it out,
saying you won't go.

559
00:27:56,590 --> 00:27:57,830
Who said I won't go?

560
00:27:59,200 --> 00:28:00,400
Five planes.

561
00:28:00,510 --> 00:28:01,270
Bro,

562
00:28:01,440 --> 00:28:02,750
the Murong family got

563
00:28:02,750 --> 00:28:04,550
all the bargains on the 5 planes.

564
00:28:04,550 --> 00:28:05,110
What,

565
00:28:05,350 --> 00:28:07,410
can't our Huo family play hard to get?

566
00:28:07,790 --> 00:28:09,720
I have to make him grovel a bit.

567
00:28:09,720 --> 00:28:11,580
Can't let him just get a free ride.

568
00:28:12,440 --> 00:28:14,350
You guys are so full of schemes.

569
00:28:16,000 --> 00:28:17,400
Shut your trap with this.

570
00:28:23,310 --> 00:28:24,040
Not bad, huh?

571
00:28:27,800 --> 00:28:31,250
[Xanadu Cabaret]

572
00:29:45,880 --> 00:29:47,590
Why's the traffic so bad?

573
00:29:47,720 --> 00:29:49,050
Do you know how to drive?

574
00:29:49,590 --> 00:29:50,830
I'm so sorry.

575
00:29:51,030 --> 00:29:52,550
I don't know what happened.

576
00:29:52,550 --> 00:29:54,160
I'm just gonna drive away.

577
00:29:54,510 --> 00:29:55,400
Sorry!

578
00:29:55,640 --> 00:29:56,480
Sorry!

579
00:30:10,110 --> 00:30:10,770
Drive away!

580
00:30:29,880 --> 00:30:30,590
Got it.

581
00:30:56,640 --> 00:30:57,270
Mrs. Wang.

582
00:30:59,920 --> 00:31:00,590
Miss Fang.

583
00:31:00,790 --> 00:31:02,250
What are you doing in here?

584
00:31:02,590 --> 00:31:03,680
I want to help out

585
00:31:03,680 --> 00:31:05,080
with the family banquet.

586
00:31:05,200 --> 00:31:06,730
I want to cook a Nanyang dish

587
00:31:06,920 --> 00:31:08,250
to make a contribution.

588
00:31:08,310 --> 00:31:09,030
Sure.

589
00:31:10,480 --> 00:31:12,070
But I'm missing a few ingredients.

590
00:31:11,220 --> 00:31:12,420
[Papaya] [Milk] [Sago]
[Condensed milk] [Honeyed red beans]

591
00:31:12,350 --> 00:31:14,080
-I need to go out...
-Miss Fang.

592
00:31:15,350 --> 00:31:17,280
What ingredients are so important

593
00:31:17,440 --> 00:31:18,700
that you must get them?

594
00:31:25,590 --> 00:31:26,310
Never mind.

595
00:31:27,720 --> 00:31:29,030
I wanted to go buy them,

596
00:31:29,640 --> 00:31:30,920
but now it seems

597
00:31:31,750 --> 00:31:34,010
the most important ingredient, papaya,

598
00:31:34,240 --> 00:31:35,570
is no longer available.

599
00:31:35,750 --> 00:31:36,680
This dish

600
00:31:37,070 --> 00:31:38,110
can't be made.

601
00:31:38,590 --> 00:31:39,720
There will be no show

602
00:31:40,310 --> 00:31:41,640
for you to watch either.

603
00:31:42,640 --> 00:31:43,370
That's fine.

604
00:31:44,510 --> 00:31:46,440
The papayas you can buy in Nancheng

605
00:31:46,550 --> 00:31:47,880
are never fresh enough.

606
00:31:48,400 --> 00:31:50,310
I have genuine papayas here.

607
00:31:51,110 --> 00:31:51,720
Later,

608
00:31:52,440 --> 00:31:54,300
I'll have Laiyi bring them to you.

609
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:28,460
All of you, get out.

610
00:32:29,440 --> 00:32:29,960
Put down

611
00:32:29,960 --> 00:32:31,000
your things now.

612
00:32:31,000 --> 00:32:31,750
Quickly.

613
00:32:41,640 --> 00:32:42,480
Ren Susu.

614
00:32:44,590 --> 00:32:46,050
You calculate every step.

615
00:32:46,750 --> 00:32:48,480
How could I not be prepared?

616
00:32:51,110 --> 00:32:51,960
What do you want?

617
00:32:51,960 --> 00:32:53,400
I should ask you that.

618
00:32:54,880 --> 00:32:55,510
What,

619
00:32:56,310 --> 00:32:57,840
afraid to see an old friend?

620
00:33:00,880 --> 00:33:02,310
Why should I be afraid?

621
00:33:04,030 --> 00:33:05,490
Are you really not afraid?

622
00:33:23,750 --> 00:33:24,790
Then what is this?

623
00:33:28,960 --> 00:33:30,350
Do you know what

624
00:33:30,880 --> 00:33:33,210
the most beautiful sound in this world is?

625
00:33:39,350 --> 00:33:41,030
Someone once told me that...

626
00:33:43,510 --> 00:33:45,440
it's the sound of fingers

627
00:33:46,510 --> 00:33:49,370
trailing across a lover's skin
in the dead of night.

628
00:33:53,720 --> 00:33:55,000
Is that so?

629
00:33:56,400 --> 00:33:57,730
It's fine if you forgot.

630
00:33:58,720 --> 00:34:00,270
I can help you remember it all,

631
00:34:00,270 --> 00:34:01,590
bit by bit.

632
00:34:04,330 --> 00:34:05,890
♪ The more passionate ♪

633
00:34:05,900 --> 00:34:08,060
♪ Our past embrace ♪

634
00:34:06,480 --> 00:34:07,550
Tonight,

635
00:34:07,960 --> 00:34:10,150
don't even think about
stepping out of this house.

636
00:34:10,150 --> 00:34:10,880
Come back in!

637
00:34:11,100 --> 00:34:12,409
♪ The more icy ♪

638
00:34:11,440 --> 00:34:12,710
Help Miss Fang cook.

639
00:34:12,510 --> 00:34:14,409
♪ Our present clash ♪

640
00:34:16,770 --> 00:34:18,639
♪ If not tangled in love ♪

641
00:34:19,830 --> 00:34:22,170
♪ We are locked in hate ♪

642
00:34:23,300 --> 00:34:27,600
♪ There is no escaping it ♪
